<title>bạlḥkmẗ ạ̹nt wḥdk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (bạlḥkmẗ ạ̹nt wḥdk .. mạsk zmạm ạlạ̉mr
 kl ạlkẖywṭ fy ydk .. wạ̉myn bṭwl ạlʿmr)2
 (lyk ạlklmẗ ạlạ̉kẖyrẗ .. mhmạ qạlwạ fklạm
 ʿạly wạ̹ydk qdyrẗ .. qlbk mlyạn ḥnạn)2
 2- (ṣạlḥ ạ̹nt wmḥsn .. ṣạlḥ bṭwl ạlʿmr
 wfy strk ạ̹nt nskn .. mhmạ ạlsnyn btmr)2
 (mhmạ ạlẓrwf tʿạnd .. wạ̹n mrt ạlạ̉zmạt
 tfḍl btqwd wsạnd .. fy ạ̉ṣʿb ạlạ̉wqạt)2
 3- (mạ btdy ạ̹lạ ạlkẖyr .. mhmạ ạlmsẖhd ẓlạm
 klh bạ̉mrk yṣyr .. dy wʿwdk msẖ klạm)2
 (tfạṣyl ạlʿmr ʿndk .. ḥạsbhạ bạlạ̹tqạn
 wḥyạty hy mlkk .. ḥbk ạ̉fḍl ḍmạn)2
 4- (ạ̹dyny ʿynyn tsẖwfk .. wtṣdq bạlạ̹ymạn
 dạ mạfysẖ ạ̉mr yfwtk .. wfy ạ̹ydk ạlslṭạn)2
 (yạ ḥbyby sạʿdny ạ̉sẖkr .. ạ̉slm wạstryḥ
 wạkẖḍʿ lk rby wạṣbr .. ạ̹nt ḥkmk ṣḥyḥ)2
 5- (ytbʿny kẖyr wrḥmẗ .. dạymaⁿạ wfy kl ywm
 ạ̹klyl ạ̹ḥsạn wrạ̉fẗ .. fwqy dạymaⁿạ ydwm)2
 (wạnạ tạyh btrạqbny .. wbtrtẖy lkl ḍʿfy
 tsẖfʿ ly wtʿạljny .. wbnʿmẗ trd nfsy)2</lyrics>
</song>